---
title: Mixed Mushroom and Chicken Breast Risotto with Fried Sage Leaves
description: This dish takes flavour inspiration from your favourite trattoria. Hearty broth plumps up each grain of rice to create an irresistibly creamy risotto topped with mouthwatering chicken. A sprinkle of fragrant, crispy sage leaves will make you feel like a top chef.
